data.description: Indulge in the lifestyle you deserve with this exceptional home in Briarwood. This exceptional home is strategically located for both convenience and tranquility, offering a lifestyle of unparalleled comfort. As you step through the 2-story entry, you'll be captivated by the seamless flow of the floor plan that guides you through every corner of this spacious residence. The grandeur of the open 2-story gathering room awaits, providing an inviting atmosphere for both relaxation and entertainment. The oversized eat-in kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting stainless appliances, granite counters, maple cabinets, and ample counter space for culinary creations. An office space adorned with built-ins, and a convenient Murphy bed for versatility, and a thoughtfully designed guest room and full bath complement the main level, providing comfort and privacy for visiting guests. Travel one of the two staircases to discover a haven of serenity on the upper level. Four additional bedrooms, including an incredible primary retreat, featuring a fireplace, a luxurious spa-like ensuite fitted with a laundry area and a closet that fulfills every wardrobe enthusiast's dream. Bedroom 3 features a luxury private bathroom with a large closet, while bedrooms 4 and 5 are adjoined with an updated jack-and-jill style ensuite. The daylight lower level adds an extra dimension to this already remarkable home. Here, you'll find the 6th and 7th bedrooms with a full bath, and an abundance of storage, including a workshop with industrial garage door opener, ensuring that every item has its place. Step outside to the rear patio overlooking a level yard and an oasis that provides the perfect setting for outdoor gatherings. Additional features of this luxurious residence include a whole-house generator, solar panels, and 100-year shingles (2021) ensuring uninterrupted comfort and peace of mind.
